          <p class="ec-cards-body"> The flagship hackathon of NITR. HackNITR is a unique platform to bring out your ideas and technological skills to build awesome projects and win exciting prizes and schwags. Visit <a href="https://hacknitr.tech/" style="color:#000000;"> hacknitr.tech</a> to stay tuned.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 animatable bounceInLeft">
        <div class="ec-cards grow-rotate">
          <h1 class="ec-cards-head">Preptember Series</h1>
          <p class="ec-cards-body">We organised a series of workshops in the month of September to train students in different skills and technologies like Git & Github, Python, JS, etc. to get them started with open-source.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 animatable bounceInRight">
        <div class="ec-cards grow-rotate">
          <h1 class="ec-cards-head">Hacktoberfest NITR</h1>
          <p class="ec-cards-body">We organise hacktoberfest meetups every year to celeberate open-source and help students get started with it. It includes interesting talks,hands on sessions and a lot of goodies and schwags to be won.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 animatable bounceInRight">
        <div class="ec-cards grow-rotate">
          <h1 class="ec-cards-head"> NITR Conclave Hackathon</h1>
          <p class="ec-cards-body">We organised this hackathon at the 9th edition of NIT Conclave.Student from different NITs across the country participated in it and presented their brilliant ideas.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
